snippet.textDisplay:
Oh my gosh....
I was here from the start. As soon as I read the title, I burst into happy tears. Watching Dan become the man and now Dad he is, was an amazing transformation. I know I’m only a young teen, but I have been watching him pretty much my entire life. He means the literal world to me.
All the fun Minecraft videos, from the coffee shop mod, to him at the orphanage horror map, I had so much fun watching his videos and spending my free time drawing fan mail. Dan, I know I’m young but I felt to need to say this. I’m very proud. I can’t wait to watch little Asher grow up and hopefully follow in his amazing Dads footsteps!


Love you Dan! Thank you for being there making me laugh through videos!🙂
